output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. CMF Number: Yes, contains "CMF 11240014" which indicates it's electoral propaganda
2. Refers to candidates: - Mentions "Florin Cornel Popovici" as AUR candidate for Chamber of Deputies - Mentions "George Simion" who is a presidential candidate - This fulfills Article 36 (7) - a
3. Addresses wide population: - It's a paid Facebook ad - Uses collective language ("să ne susținem unii pe alții") - Clearly addresses a wide audience - The estimated audience size is over 1 million people
4. Electoral objective: - Explicitly states candidacy for Chamber of Deputies - Seeks support for both parliamentary and presidential positions - Mentions fighting corruption and changing the country - Clear electoral messaging
5. Journalism vs Propaganda: - This is clearly campaign material, not journalism - Contains personal promises and campaign messaging - Has official CMF number
6. Personal opinion: - While including personal statements, this is clearly structured as campaign material - The format and delivery indicate organized political messaging

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: 1. It has an official CMF number 2. It explicitly promotes both parliamentary and presidential candidates 3. It's a paid advertisement reaching a large audience 4. Contains clear electoral messaging and calls for support 5. Is funded by a third party (TOP DUO CONSULTING S.R.L.)
conclusion.message-for-police: TOP DUO CONSULTING S.R.L., pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin promovarea unui mesaj de propaganda electorala (ID Facebook: 914473200271350) ce face referire directă și pozitivă la candidatul prezidențial George Simion, după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024. Mesajul, care include numărul CMF 11240014, reprezintă o continuare a propagandei electorale după încheierea perioadei legale pentru alegerile prezidențiale, fiind distribuit ca reclamă plătită pe Facebook cu un impact potențial de peste 1 milion de persoane. Conținutul promovează explicit candidatul la președinție într-un context electoral, încălcând astfel prevederile legale privind perioada de campanie.
